name: Defibrillators Def. Defi Defth - Los Angeles (Formerly Stl)
description:
Screams fall on def ears. Little dogs sic balls. Feet gone. Guts. Your blood pools up. You slide into it like a hot tub, hooking your elbows over the sides so you can reach your Jack 'n Coke. A show of force overcomes your deficits. Resurrections are the definition of small miracles. The game’s on the big screen. Go on and root for your favorite team! (Even if they leave town...)
